      "name": "Grid convergence index study — rotating impeller passage",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study on the impeller passage and volute. GCI for NIH quantity of interest: 9.1% on fine mesh. Discretization error exceeds the required threshold for MRL 5 but is documented as a known gap."
    }
