      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis model (Giersiepen power law) used without comparison to alternative formulations (e.g., Wriggers, Taskin). Model form uncertainty not quantified. Not assessed; flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
