      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed with 1,200 samples propagating uncertainty in viscosity, hematocrit, power-law stress exponent, and material constants. Output variance reported as aggregate 95% interval. The UQ report notes that a sensitivity analysis to rank input contributions is planned as a follow-on activity but has not been completed; dominant drivers are therefore uncharacterized. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
